{"tid":2122790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據悉港鐵有維修工人及學徒感染新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-07-24T07:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:48:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcb174cf6f054e318ee512b8632c892f6d43082","tid":2122790,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"港鐵通知員工，一名在屯門車廠工作的維修技工初步確診，他星期二起已沒有上班。這名技工的家人早前已確診，港鐵已徹底消毒屯門車廠的工場範圍、休息室及更衣室。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名港島綫及將軍澳綫車站維修學徒早上通知港鐵自己確診，由於他的家人早前也確診，他獲安排入住檢疫設施。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，港鐵已追蹤兩人在公司的密切接觸者，並安排他們留在家中，等待衞生防護中心的安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399174&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=545661a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399174&h=87489051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399174</a>"},{"pid":"8ec1c4dcda5574fade559043b1814d343e9e3a75","tid":2122790,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"港鐵員工好黃"},{"pid":"0857cdb6b68a9dda86d97020008bf1744e6d31d6","tid":2122790,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"黃到染病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}